        {
            "title": "中行首季稅後利潤升4.17% 不良貸款率微降",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國銀行(03988)公布，截至2026年3月31日止首季股東應享稅後利潤566.31億元(人民幣．下同)，按年升4.17%；每股基本盈利0.18元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中國銀行 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_03988-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中國銀行 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250410_FI_source-ap_03988-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中國銀行 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">營業收入1788.22億元，按年增長8.44%。淨利息收入1161.43 億元，按年增長7.81%。淨息差1.26%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">非利息收入626.79億元，按年增長9.61%，非利息收入在營業收入中佔比為35.05%。其中，手續費及佣金收支淨額270.82億元，按年增長5.58%；其他非利息收入合計355.97億元，按年增長12.89%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">營業費用658.99億元，按年增加10.55%。成本收入比24.8%。集團資產減值損失382.86億元，按年增加60.40億元，增長18.73%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">不良貸款總額2970.11億元，不良貸款率1.22%，比上年末下降0.01個百分點，不良貸款撥備覆蓋率203.17%，比上年末上升2.80個百分點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">核心一級資本充足率為12.18%，一級資本充足率為13.92%，資本充足率為18.23%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15939395-%e4%b8%ad%e8%a1%8c%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%a8%85%e5%be%8c%e5%88%a9%e6%bd%a4%e5%8d%874-17-%e4%b8%8d%e8%89%af%e8%b2%b8%e6%ac%be%e7%8e%87%e5%be%ae%e9%99%8d",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20230719_FI_source_licensed_03988_shutterstock_704.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-29 18:21:54",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
